1
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:38,640
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:41,220
=Episode 32=

3
00:00:43,166 --> 00:00:44,291
All by yourself,

4
00:00:46,416 --> 00:00:48,583
can you stand against this rotten world?

5
00:00:49,791 --> 00:00:50,625
Maybe not.

6
00:00:52,125 --> 00:00:53,541
There was a time

7
00:00:54,958 --> 00:00:56,166
when I wanted to drown myself
in wine and dreams

8
00:00:57,500 --> 00:00:58,541
and run from everything.

9
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:04,958
But for you,

10
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:07,708
I'm willing to try.

11
00:01:10,750 --> 00:01:11,416
Really?

12
00:01:15,125 --> 00:01:15,666
Really.

13
00:01:18,041 --> 00:01:18,875
I will help you.

14
00:01:22,583 --> 00:01:24,208
Together, we will leave

15
00:01:29,125 --> 00:01:30,208
one clean mark on this rotten world.

16
00:01:36,166 --> 00:01:36,500
Hua.

17
00:01:37,333 --> 00:01:39,125
You are still badly wounded.
Why are you out here?

18
00:01:40,541 --> 00:01:41,791
I came to see you.

19
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,500
Guan Yunfeng liked drinking alone.

20
00:01:46,791 --> 00:01:48,083
You are keeping him company, are you?

21
00:01:50,333 --> 00:01:51,250
I'm fine.

22
00:01:52,625 --> 00:01:53,833
The dead are gone.

23
00:01:54,708 --> 00:01:55,458
Those of us still alive

24
00:01:56,958 --> 00:01:58,041
cannot give up on ourselves.

25
00:01:59,833 --> 00:02:00,541
Otherwise,

26
00:02:01,875 --> 00:02:04,166
we would be wasting the life
Guan Yunfeng gave his own to save.

27
00:02:04,625 --> 00:02:05,250
Yes.

28
00:02:06,916 --> 00:02:08,458
I will carry out Guan's last wish

29
00:02:09,166 --> 00:02:09,958
and capture Leng Xin.

30
00:02:10,916 --> 00:02:11,666
Well said.

31
00:02:12,666 --> 00:02:13,458
Feng Fuliu?

32
00:02:14,166 --> 00:02:14,583
Feng Fuliu?

33
00:02:14,750 --> 00:02:15,291
Come with me.

34
00:02:19,666 --> 00:02:21,708
Are you Feng Fuliu, or Chang Beiming
in disguise?

35
00:02:22,291 --> 00:02:23,291
Truth or lies...

36
00:02:24,291 --> 00:02:25,291
Would you believe anything I say?

37
00:02:26,333 --> 00:02:27,041
Feng Fuliu.

38
00:02:27,833 --> 00:02:28,666
You are dead in the records.

39
00:02:29,083 --> 00:02:29,666
Your case is closed.

40
00:02:30,458 --> 00:02:31,125
Turn back while you can.

41
00:02:31,125 --> 00:02:32,083
Leave this life behind.

42
00:02:32,708 --> 00:02:34,458
There are still too many true villains

43
00:02:34,833 --> 00:02:35,541
walking free.

44
00:02:36,875 --> 00:02:38,250
This world still needs
a phantom thief like me.

45
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:39,666
Then I will still have to catch you.

46
00:02:40,083 --> 00:02:40,916
Before you catch me,

47
00:02:41,333 --> 00:02:42,833
find the traitor inside the Jinyiwei.

48
00:02:43,458 --> 00:02:44,791
How do you know there is a traitor
in the Jinyiwei?

49
00:02:44,875 --> 00:02:46,458
The villa you hid in

50
00:02:47,166 --> 00:02:48,083
was supposed to be secret.

51
00:02:48,416 --> 00:02:49,750
How did the Five Armies Command
find out?

52
00:02:50,333 --> 00:02:51,708
Gao Tianxi was in prison.

53
00:02:52,041 --> 00:02:52,875
Prince Fu planned it from
behind the scenes.

54
00:02:53,333 --> 00:02:54,541
Who carried messages between them?

55
00:02:54,958 --> 00:02:56,458
Who moved official troops
like pieces on a board?

56
00:02:57,083 --> 00:02:59,041
Leng Xin was hiding in Meizhen House.

57
00:02:59,625 --> 00:03:00,833
Where is he now?

58
00:03:01,375 --> 00:03:02,375
Until these questions are answered,

59
00:03:02,541 --> 00:03:03,750
you will never find the truth.

60
00:03:10,125 --> 00:03:12,750
You want to interrogate Wang Yan?

61
00:03:13,166 --> 00:03:15,125
Wang Yan knew what happened
in Prince Luo's case.

62
00:03:15,875 --> 00:03:17,291
I request permission to question him
alone.

63
00:03:18,125 --> 00:03:18,833
Bring Wang Yan in.

64
00:03:19,666 --> 00:03:20,083
Kneel.

65
00:03:21,833 --> 00:03:22,250
Wang Yan.

66
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:25,000
I have questions
about an old unsolved case.

67
00:03:25,166 --> 00:03:26,708
What crappy old case?

68
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,625
I know nothing!

69
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,166
Seven years ago,

70
00:03:29,291 --> 00:03:30,125
Prince Luo committed treason.

71
00:03:30,875 --> 00:03:33,083
Shen Lian was ordered
to escort a witness to the capital.

72
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:34,708
Then he was assassinated.

73
00:03:35,166 --> 00:03:36,375
Do you know anything about that?

74
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:37,291
Who are you?

75
00:03:38,333 --> 00:03:39,125
All of you, leave us.

76
00:03:39,458 --> 00:03:39,875
Yes.

77
00:03:43,958 --> 00:03:45,125
I'm Shen Lian's daughter.

78
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:53,083
Shen Lian's daughter?

79
00:03:54,125 --> 00:03:54,458
Yes.

80
00:03:56,166 --> 00:03:58,458
I will uncover the truth
and clear my father's name.

81
00:03:58,833 --> 00:03:59,875
Then it seems

82
00:03:59,875 --> 00:04:01,041
you know nothing about what happened.

83
00:04:03,166 --> 00:04:04,416
Were you the traitor?

84
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:06,458
Yes.

85
00:04:07,375 --> 00:04:08,458
But I was not the mastermind.

86
00:04:09,125 --> 00:04:09,833
Who was it?

87
00:04:11,083 --> 00:04:13,166
The true mastermind was your father,

88
00:04:13,166 --> 00:04:14,541
Qianhu Shen Lian!

89
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:21,833
Taozi.

90
00:04:23,583 --> 00:04:24,208
Hua.

91
00:04:29,291 --> 00:04:29,875
Taozi.

92
00:04:34,333 --> 00:04:34,833
Hua.

93
00:04:35,666 --> 00:04:37,041
Taozi was trafficked as a child.

94
00:04:37,458 --> 00:04:38,208
She has no family.

95
00:04:38,875 --> 00:04:39,666
She has had a hard life.

96
00:04:39,958 --> 00:04:41,791
So what exactly are you doing

97
00:04:41,791 --> 00:04:43,416
keeping her at Chong'er Pavilion?

98
00:04:44,375 --> 00:04:47,041
I haven't decided where to send her yet.

99
00:04:47,625 --> 00:04:49,458
Then you had better think it through.

100
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,666
Don't get in the way of her future.

101
00:04:58,500 --> 00:04:59,250
Xintian.

102
00:04:59,541 --> 00:05:00,458
Does Hua

103
00:05:01,208 --> 00:05:02,375
not like me?

104
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:04,375
Of course not.

105
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:05,416
Nonsense!

106
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:07,208
The court is now split
into two factions.

107
00:05:08,125 --> 00:05:08,875
The Crown Prince's faction

108
00:05:09,291 --> 00:05:10,041
and Prince Fu's faction.

109
00:05:10,125 --> 00:05:12,041
Almost every official at court

110
00:05:12,041 --> 00:05:13,208
belongs to one of them.

111
00:05:13,541 --> 00:05:14,750
So do you really think

112
00:05:15,708 --> 00:05:16,500
your father was innocent?

113
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:18,708
Which faction was my father in?

114
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,500
Prince Fu's.

115
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:20,500
You are lying!

116
00:05:20,833 --> 00:05:21,291
Back then,

117
00:05:21,666 --> 00:05:23,291
His Majesty delayed
naming a Crown Prince.

118
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,875
The Eldest Prince and the Third Prince,

119
00:05:25,166 --> 00:05:27,625
now known as the Crown Prince
and Prince Fu,

120
00:05:28,041 --> 00:05:29,416
fought over the succession

121
00:05:29,666 --> 00:05:32,208
until their open and hidden battles
brought misery to the people.

122
00:05:32,583 --> 00:05:33,291
And His Majesty?

123
00:05:33,958 --> 00:05:35,000
He favored Prince Fu.

124
00:05:36,041 --> 00:05:38,833
But the ministers followed
the ancestral rule

125
00:05:39,083 --> 00:05:40,208
and supported the Eldest Prince.

126
00:05:40,625 --> 00:05:42,041
You know what happened after that.

127
00:05:42,458 --> 00:05:43,416
Prince Luo rebelled.

128
00:05:43,833 --> 00:05:46,041
He claimed he was acting in support
of the Eldest Prince.

129
00:05:46,541 --> 00:05:47,125
But in truth,

130
00:05:47,125 --> 00:05:49,625
it was a desperate move
by Prince Luo and Prince Fu.

131
00:05:49,916 --> 00:05:50,458
The goal

132
00:05:50,625 --> 00:05:53,000
was to use the rebellion to bring down
the Crown Prince for good.

133
00:05:53,166 --> 00:05:54,666
But Prince Luo

134
00:05:55,625 --> 00:05:57,416
was a fool.

135
00:05:57,666 --> 00:05:58,500
Before he could even rise,

136
00:05:59,041 --> 00:05:59,916
someone exposed him.

137
00:06:00,333 --> 00:06:01,083
Once the plot was uncovered,

138
00:06:01,791 --> 00:06:02,833
Prince Luo killed himself.

139
00:06:03,333 --> 00:06:04,833
Do you know who exposed him?

140
00:06:06,291 --> 00:06:08,083
The Chief Secretary
of his own household,

141
00:06:08,583 --> 00:06:09,416
Xu Wenchang.

142
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:12,958
The witness my father escorted...

143
00:06:13,958 --> 00:06:15,041
They called it an escort.

144
00:06:15,791 --> 00:06:17,875
But the truth was, Xu Wenchang held

145
00:06:17,875 --> 00:06:20,041
ironclad proof that Prince Luo
and Prince Fu had conspired in treason.

146
00:06:20,250 --> 00:06:22,041
If he brought that evidence
to the capital,

147
00:06:22,041 --> 00:06:24,500
Prince Fu's faction would be destroyed.

148
00:06:24,958 --> 00:06:26,625
So Prince Fu's men decided

149
00:06:27,041 --> 00:06:28,125
to kill Xu Wenchang

150
00:06:28,791 --> 00:06:30,708
on the road to the capital
and destroy the evidence.

151
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:34,041
Then my father...

152
00:06:34,333 --> 00:06:35,916
Your father was the one sent

153
00:06:35,916 --> 00:06:37,208
to kill Xu Wenchang.

154
00:06:37,375 --> 00:06:37,875
Impossible.

155
00:06:38,666 --> 00:06:40,500
My father was ordered to escort
the witness to the capital.

156
00:06:41,083 --> 00:06:42,166
Leng Xin was the killer.

157
00:06:42,250 --> 00:06:44,500
Then how do you explain
the three wrong maps?

158
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:47,291
If we had met your father

159
00:06:47,291 --> 00:06:48,708
as planned that day,

160
00:06:48,833 --> 00:06:49,333
and the three of us,

161
00:06:49,375 --> 00:06:51,125
your father, Lu Guokai, and I,

162
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:52,375
had joined forces,

163
00:06:52,625 --> 00:06:53,666
would Leng Xin have stood a chance?

164
00:06:56,833 --> 00:06:57,875
I might as well tell you.

165
00:06:57,916 --> 00:06:59,166
Back then, your father

166
00:06:59,875 --> 00:07:02,708
led the escort taking Xu Wenchang
and his wife to the capital.

167
00:07:03,625 --> 00:07:05,416
And the Jinyiwei Commander at the time

168
00:07:06,333 --> 00:07:07,583
was on the Crown Prince's side.

169
00:07:07,916 --> 00:07:10,250
Chang Beixiao, Duke Zheng's eldest son?

170
00:07:10,625 --> 00:07:11,250
Correct.

171
00:07:11,583 --> 00:07:13,041
But that Commander

172
00:07:13,041 --> 00:07:14,333
is a ruined man now.

173
00:07:14,500 --> 00:07:15,166
No point mentioning him.

174
00:07:15,791 --> 00:07:18,000
Because Zhang Weimin was also
part of the plan.

175
00:07:18,875 --> 00:07:19,958
He was with the Crown Prince too.

176
00:07:21,375 --> 00:07:22,791
(We must do this well for Prince Fu.)

177
00:07:23,333 --> 00:07:24,125
(We cannot fail him.)

178
00:07:24,666 --> 00:07:26,583
(Xu Wenchang is only a scholar.)

179
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,500
(Why not kill him on the road
and be done with it?)

180
00:07:29,916 --> 00:07:30,333
(No.)

181
00:07:31,041 --> 00:07:32,083
(Everyone at court knows)

182
00:07:32,625 --> 00:07:33,583
(we are escorting him to the capital.)

183
00:07:33,958 --> 00:07:36,958
(If something happens on the road,
suspicion falls on us.)

184
00:07:38,333 --> 00:07:40,166
(The Commander sides
with the Crown Prince.)

185
00:07:41,416 --> 00:07:43,208
(He assigned Lu Guokai to travel
with us.)

186
00:07:43,791 --> 00:07:44,375
(In truth,)

187
00:07:45,166 --> 00:07:46,291
(he is there to watch us.)

188
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:46,916
(So,)

189
00:07:47,416 --> 00:07:48,708
(we cannot afford a single mistake.)

190
00:07:49,375 --> 00:07:49,750
(Otherwise,)

191
00:07:51,416 --> 00:07:52,833
(Prince Fu will be implicated.)

192
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,541
(Qianhu Shen, here are three maps.)

193
00:07:57,125 --> 00:07:59,041
(Each marks a different time and place,)

194
00:07:59,625 --> 00:08:01,375
(but all are clear.)

195
00:08:02,333 --> 00:08:04,375
(Choose one route)

196
00:08:04,375 --> 00:08:05,333
(from these three maps.)

197
00:08:05,708 --> 00:08:07,250
(And of course,)

198
00:08:07,250 --> 00:08:08,583
(don't tell me which one.)

199
00:08:09,583 --> 00:08:11,791
(Then proceed according to plan.)

200
00:08:13,250 --> 00:08:13,583
(Yes.)

201
00:08:13,958 --> 00:08:15,500
(I chose the map)

202
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:16,166
(with the best rendezvous time
and place.)

203
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,500
(I made three copies.)

204
00:08:19,416 --> 00:08:20,666
(Each of us will hold one.)

205
00:08:21,541 --> 00:08:22,208
(You will meet me)

206
00:08:22,458 --> 00:08:24,083
(at the time and place marked on it.)

207
00:08:24,541 --> 00:08:25,291
(That is our rendezvous.)

208
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:26,208
(Shen.)

209
00:08:26,708 --> 00:08:28,541
(Since Prince Luo has already
been punished,)

210
00:08:28,958 --> 00:08:30,791
(why not escort Xu Wenchang
and his wife openly?)

211
00:08:31,041 --> 00:08:33,125
(Moving a large escort
draws too much attention.)

212
00:08:33,625 --> 00:08:34,166
(At court,)

213
00:08:34,541 --> 00:08:35,750
(there are far too many people)

214
00:08:36,458 --> 00:08:37,458
(who want Xu dead.)

215
00:08:38,083 --> 00:08:39,541
(Then why do the three of us split up)

216
00:08:39,625 --> 00:08:40,541
(instead of moving together?)

217
00:08:41,166 --> 00:08:42,666
(Jinyiwei obey orders.)

218
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,541
(Aren't you asking too many questions?)

219
00:08:47,583 --> 00:08:48,875
(Because on this journey,)

220
00:08:49,208 --> 00:08:50,250
(Xu Wenchang will talk.)

221
00:08:51,083 --> 00:08:51,833
(And what he says)

222
00:08:52,375 --> 00:08:52,916
(should be heard)

223
00:08:53,666 --> 00:08:54,625
(by as few people as possible.)

224
00:08:57,250 --> 00:08:57,916
(I understand.)

225
00:08:59,958 --> 00:09:01,166
Lu Guokai served the Crown Prince?

226
00:09:01,458 --> 00:09:02,916
Lu Guokai was lowborn.

227
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:04,541
He had no roots at court.

228
00:09:05,208 --> 00:09:06,500
No one knew whose man he really was.

229
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:07,583
So you were all guarding against him.

230
00:09:07,833 --> 00:09:09,333
My father really switched
the route maps?

231
00:09:09,541 --> 00:09:11,791
Your father commanded
the entire operation.

232
00:09:11,833 --> 00:09:13,375
Who else could have done it?

233
00:09:13,708 --> 00:09:14,833
You were allies.

234
00:09:15,125 --> 00:09:16,291
Why didn't you go to meet him?

235
00:09:16,291 --> 00:09:18,166
I went at the appointed time.

236
00:09:18,375 --> 00:09:19,916
But Leng Xin came first,

237
00:09:19,916 --> 00:09:21,208
under orders from who knows where.

238
00:09:22,083 --> 00:09:22,958
By the time I arrived,

239
00:09:23,416 --> 00:09:25,541
the ground was covered with bodies.

240
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,000
If what you say is true,

241
00:09:28,458 --> 00:09:29,958
why didn't you avenge my father?

242
00:09:31,333 --> 00:09:31,875
Bingfan.

243
00:09:32,791 --> 00:09:34,250
Why do you still not understand?

244
00:09:34,625 --> 00:09:36,166
Even if Leng Xin had never appeared,

245
00:09:36,625 --> 00:09:39,041
Xu Wenchang and his wife would
never have reached the capital alive.

246
00:09:39,875 --> 00:09:41,916
This involved Prince Fu's
deepest secrets.

247
00:09:42,083 --> 00:09:43,875
Anyone who knew the truth
would be killed.

248
00:09:44,208 --> 00:09:46,458
We all went into it ready to die.

249
00:09:47,458 --> 00:09:48,791
But whatever his reasons,

250
00:09:50,875 --> 00:09:51,916
your father saved my life.

251
00:09:55,416 --> 00:09:56,666
I just never imagined

252
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,166
that after all these years,

253
00:10:01,375 --> 00:10:03,375
the master your father risked his life
to protect

254
00:10:05,083 --> 00:10:06,375
would be brought down overnight

255
00:10:07,791 --> 00:10:08,916
by his own daughter.

256
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:10,875
Prince Fu is foolish and cruel.

257
00:10:11,666 --> 00:10:12,791
He is not fit to be emperor.

258
00:10:13,208 --> 00:10:14,666
And the Crown Prince is weak
and useless.

259
00:10:14,666 --> 00:10:15,750
Is he fit to be emperor?

260
00:10:17,791 --> 00:10:18,208
Fine.

261
00:10:19,083 --> 00:10:20,458
If what you say is true,

262
00:10:21,083 --> 00:10:21,958
do you have proof?

263
00:10:25,458 --> 00:10:26,791
Where is the official robe I wore
when I was arrested?

264
00:10:27,875 --> 00:10:28,791
In the Jinyiwei Evidence Room.

265
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:29,791
Fetch my robe.

266
00:10:30,375 --> 00:10:31,125
Cut open the lining.

267
00:10:32,208 --> 00:10:33,125
There are two maps inside.

268
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,666
One is the route map your father
gave me.

269
00:10:35,875 --> 00:10:36,791
The other was his own.

270
00:10:37,250 --> 00:10:39,125
See for yourself whether they match.

271
00:11:05,930 --> 00:11:08,140
(Rendezvous: 7-9 a.m.
Rendezvous: 5-7 a.m.)

272
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,000
(Rendezvous: 5-7 a.m.)

273
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:11,833
(Rendezvous: 5-7 a.m.)
Rendezvous at 5-7 a.m.

274
00:11:13,430 --> 00:11:14,333
(Rendezvous: 7-9 a.m.)

275
00:11:14,333 --> 00:11:15,333
(Rendezvous: 7-9 a.m.)
Rendezvous at 7-9 a.m.

276
00:11:15,810 --> 00:11:18,970
(Rendezvous: 7-9 a.m.
Rendezvous: 5-7 a.m.)

277
00:11:31,166 --> 00:11:32,333
Where do you think

278
00:11:34,083 --> 00:11:35,458
Leng Xin is hiding?

279
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:38,416
Could it be

280
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,083
that he was never
in Meizhen House at all?

281
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:41,416
No.

282
00:11:42,291 --> 00:11:43,208
Before I left,

283
00:11:43,458 --> 00:11:44,500
Prince Fu said it himself.

284
00:11:46,291 --> 00:11:47,458
But we searched all of Meizhen House

285
00:11:48,083 --> 00:11:48,875
and found nothing.

286
00:11:49,333 --> 00:11:50,000
Could he have been hiding

287
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,708
among the soldiers
who attacked the villa?

288
00:11:52,083 --> 00:11:53,500
None of those soldiers had skill
like that.

289
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:54,583
How could Guan Yunfeng

290
00:11:55,375 --> 00:11:57,458
have been killed so suddenly by Du Bin?

291
00:11:58,083 --> 00:11:59,250
These days,

292
00:12:00,416 --> 00:12:02,041
I almost don't recognize myself.

293
00:12:03,166 --> 00:12:04,041
Why do you say that?

294
00:12:05,250 --> 00:12:06,000
Before,

295
00:12:06,291 --> 00:12:07,666
I was always afraid.

296
00:12:08,458 --> 00:12:09,166
But lately,

297
00:12:10,458 --> 00:12:11,333
I feel calm.

298
00:12:13,958 --> 00:12:14,416
Taozi.

299
00:12:15,583 --> 00:12:16,791
Stay with me from now on,

300
00:12:17,333 --> 00:12:18,625
and you won't have to live
in fear anymore.

301
00:12:22,833 --> 00:12:23,416
Xintian.

302
00:12:24,625 --> 00:12:25,791
Do you have someone you like?

303
00:12:31,250 --> 00:12:32,458
But he is gone now.

304
00:12:35,458 --> 00:12:36,041
Well...

305
00:12:36,916 --> 00:12:38,083
Do you have someone you hate?

306
00:12:39,458 --> 00:12:39,875
Yes.

307
00:12:41,541 --> 00:12:42,041
Leng Xin.

308
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:23,833
There is a hidden chamber in your room.

309
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:24,916
So what?

310
00:13:25,208 --> 00:13:26,333
I want to see it.

311
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:26,916
You?

312
00:13:27,458 --> 00:13:28,000
On what grounds?

313
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:29,083
On the grounds

314
00:13:30,708 --> 00:13:31,833
that I'm Shen Lian's daughter.

315
00:13:39,333 --> 00:13:39,958
Bingfan.

316
00:13:40,958 --> 00:13:42,000
Kowtow to your father.

317
00:13:51,140 --> 00:13:54,560
(Spirit Tablet of My Sworn Brother,
Qianhu, Shen Lian)

318
00:13:58,291 --> 00:13:58,875
Take a look.

319
00:14:10,625 --> 00:14:11,083
(Just as I thought.)

320
00:14:11,833 --> 00:14:13,458
(Lu Guokai's route map was different.)

321
00:14:14,208 --> 00:14:16,041
(Wang Yan's map matched my father's.)

322
00:14:16,583 --> 00:14:18,416
(Only the rendezvous time
was delayed by one hour.)

323
00:14:20,916 --> 00:14:22,958
(Was father really trying
to send them away on purpose,)

324
00:14:24,125 --> 00:14:25,291
(so they would not come
to the rendezvous?)

325
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:27,916
Mr. Lu.

326
00:14:31,458 --> 00:14:32,166
You said

327
00:14:32,833 --> 00:14:34,666
the three maps my father gave out
were all different.

328
00:14:34,791 --> 00:14:36,166
But my father's map

329
00:14:36,166 --> 00:14:37,000
was the same as Wang Yan's.

330
00:14:37,083 --> 00:14:38,250
I never saw

331
00:14:38,250 --> 00:14:38,833
Wang Yan's map.

332
00:14:39,208 --> 00:14:40,833
I only knew Wang Yan did not arrive
on time.

333
00:14:41,166 --> 00:14:42,541
So I thought...

334
00:14:45,583 --> 00:14:46,125
No.

335
00:14:47,875 --> 00:14:49,583
They were guarding against me.

336
00:14:51,166 --> 00:14:52,541
If Wang Yan had the right map,

337
00:14:52,875 --> 00:14:53,833
why didn't he arrive?

338
00:14:54,083 --> 00:14:55,250
Because his rendezvous time

339
00:14:56,041 --> 00:14:57,333
was delayed by one hour.

340
00:14:58,708 --> 00:14:59,416
Your father

341
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,458
was deliberately keeping us away.

342
00:15:06,583 --> 00:15:08,083
Whatever your father was doing
back then,

343
00:15:10,083 --> 00:15:11,625
he was saving our lives.

344
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:15,416
That is why, when you first
joined the Jinyiwei,

345
00:15:15,416 --> 00:15:16,750
I tried everything to block you
and make things difficult.

346
00:15:16,791 --> 00:15:19,500
I didn't want you dragged
into this mess.

347
00:15:21,833 --> 00:15:22,666
And after that?

348
00:15:25,166 --> 00:15:25,958
After that,

349
00:15:26,333 --> 00:15:27,125
I realized

350
00:15:27,125 --> 00:15:28,166
you had real potential.

351
00:15:28,916 --> 00:15:29,708
So

352
00:15:30,041 --> 00:15:31,208
I wanted to train you

353
00:15:31,208 --> 00:15:32,375
into a true Jinyiwei.

354
00:15:35,583 --> 00:15:36,666
But my father said

355
00:15:37,458 --> 00:15:38,708
there was a traitor inside the Jinyiwei.

356
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:42,541
At court,

357
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,500
everyone belongs either
to the Crown Prince or Prince Fu.

358
00:15:44,833 --> 00:15:46,958
When loyalties differ,
anyone can look like a traitor.

359
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:48,541
But I cannot accept that.

360
00:15:48,958 --> 00:15:49,958
Now that Wang Yan is dead,

361
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:51,916
you have no evidence left.

362
00:15:51,958 --> 00:15:54,458
Do you really think a few maps

363
00:15:54,458 --> 00:15:55,958
are enough to overturn the case?

364
00:15:59,458 --> 00:16:02,583
(Northern Bureau)

365
00:16:02,583 --> 00:16:04,383
(Northern Bureau)
(Let this matter go.)

366
00:16:04,383 --> 00:16:05,166
(Northern Bureau)
(Maybe)

367
00:16:05,583 --> 00:16:06,458
(Northern Bureau)
(not finding the truth)

368
00:16:06,458 --> 00:16:07,991
(Northern Bureau)
(is the best outcome.)

369
00:16:07,991 --> 00:16:10,375
(Northern Bureau)
(So the truth I spent my life chasing)

370
00:16:12,041 --> 00:16:13,416
(is this cruel.)

371
00:16:13,875 --> 00:16:15,333
(Wang Yan will be executed
after autumn.)

372
00:16:15,625 --> 00:16:17,583
(The truth will be buried forever.)

373
00:16:18,041 --> 00:16:18,750
(What about Leng Xin?)

374
00:16:19,333 --> 00:16:20,541
(He is only a killing machine.)

375
00:16:20,791 --> 00:16:21,541
(He does not matter.)

376
00:16:42,458 --> 00:16:43,708
Didn't you once say

377
00:16:45,458 --> 00:16:47,625
you would pay any price
to uncover the truth?

378
00:16:50,166 --> 00:16:51,291
That whatever the ending was,

379
00:16:51,916 --> 00:16:53,083
you would face it bravely?

380
00:16:54,333 --> 00:16:55,375
Why go back on your word

381
00:16:56,041 --> 00:16:56,791
and leave the capital?

382
00:16:57,875 --> 00:16:58,708
Because the truth

383
00:17:00,291 --> 00:17:01,458
has gone far beyond

384
00:17:01,458 --> 00:17:02,458
what I can bear.

385
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:03,750
I'm afraid.

386
00:17:04,166 --> 00:17:04,708
I'm tired of it.

387
00:17:05,250 --> 00:17:05,750
I'm exhausted.

388
00:17:06,375 --> 00:17:07,125
I want to leave.

389
00:17:09,041 --> 00:17:10,208
What about why you started?

390
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:12,416
Your purpose?

391
00:17:13,875 --> 00:17:15,166
Your justice?

392
00:17:15,916 --> 00:17:16,500
Fake.

393
00:17:17,791 --> 00:17:18,375
All of it.

394
00:17:20,125 --> 00:17:20,541
Fine.

395
00:17:21,791 --> 00:17:23,000
What about Hua and Xintian?

396
00:17:23,416 --> 00:17:24,041
You are leaving them too?

397
00:17:25,416 --> 00:17:26,250
What about Guan Yunfeng's death?

398
00:17:26,541 --> 00:17:27,541
You will not avenge him?

399
00:17:28,291 --> 00:17:29,750
Leng Xin is still out there.

400
00:17:30,625 --> 00:17:31,541
You will stop hunting him?

401
00:17:32,291 --> 00:17:32,916
I cannot care anymore.

402
00:17:37,458 --> 00:17:38,166
And me?

403
00:17:39,458 --> 00:17:40,416
Are you leaving me too?

404
00:17:42,833 --> 00:17:43,958
Then say I failed you.

405
00:17:47,041 --> 00:17:47,750
Shen Bingfan.

406
00:17:48,666 --> 00:17:50,250
Even if I have to force you,

407
00:17:51,791 --> 00:17:52,916
I will keep you here today.

408
00:17:53,333 --> 00:17:54,833
Then, you are asking me to die.

409
00:18:02,916 --> 00:18:03,458
Beiming.

410
00:18:05,958 --> 00:18:07,458
When I first came
to the Northern Bureau,

411
00:18:08,458 --> 00:18:09,166
you were the one

412
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:10,791
who cherished me most.

413
00:18:14,791 --> 00:18:16,750
I once wanted to spend my life
choosing you above all others.

414
00:18:20,958 --> 00:18:23,041
But I cannot stay in this place
of endless ruin.

415
00:18:24,750 --> 00:18:25,750
So, say I failed you.

416
00:18:28,500 --> 00:18:29,291
I don't want you to go!

417
00:18:48,140 --> 00:18:51,310
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

418
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:55,060
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

419
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:58,310
♪My heart drifted lost♪

420
00:18:58,310 --> 00:19:01,720
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

421
00:19:02,810 --> 00:19:06,020
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

422
00:19:06,430 --> 00:19:09,770
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

423
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:12,560
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

424
00:19:12,560 --> 00:19:16,600
♪I've softly let it go♪

425
00:19:16,600 --> 00:19:20,470
♪The vow you made was true♪

426
00:19:20,470 --> 00:19:24,220
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

427
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:26,430
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

428
00:19:26,430 --> 00:19:30,970
♪And forget at world's end♪

429
00:19:31,270 --> 00:19:32,770
♪Embracing memory♪

430
00:19:32,770 --> 00:19:35,140
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

431
00:19:35,140 --> 00:19:39,020
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

432
00:19:39,020 --> 00:19:41,350
♪I wish to let it pass♪

433
00:19:41,350 --> 00:19:46,350
♪And run toward this vast life♪
